  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lxqt-admin</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lxqt-admin</application> package provides two GUI tools to
adjust settings of the operating system <application>LXQt</application> is
running on.
    </para>

    &lfs120_checked;

